    <note>Li(2) Zhaosu(2) [19574] According to the biography of his great great grandson, Heng [7276], he was an investigating censor, but does not appear as such in the HuangSong Shichao gangyao lists. It is within the range of chronological logic that this is the same man as the Xinghua jun, Putian county Zhaosu [16983] and that a descendant moved to Yangzhou. Zhaosu might also be his zi and he may be kin with Ding [1097] and Cha [970], and other Yangzhou, Jiangdu Li(2) lineage members. He also might be the military officer cited in CBD, 2, 1007.</note>
